name: USA NFT
description:
NFT country of the USA. The base is made of the highest quality raw gold. Stand made of Sequoia and Silver wood. On a stand are some famous buildings and one not quite building. USA. List of buildings: 1.White House 2.Empire state building
3.Golden gate bridge 4.Washington Monument 5.Flatiron Building, 6.United States Capitol 7.John Hancock Center
8. SpaceX CEO Elon Musk rocket. The Statue of Liberty rides and rotates along it with the help of a mechanism, Also at the top is guarded by the Bald Eagle, the symbol of America.
On the back there is a silver emblem of the Statue of Liberty
